"      Lancefield RC. A SEROLOGICAL DIFFERENTIATION OF SPECIFIC TYPES OF BOVINE HEMOLYTIC STREPTOCOCCI (GROUP B). J Exp Med 1934; 59:441.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
