"      Jennings HJ, Katzenellenbogen E, Lugowski C, Kasper DL. Structure of native polysaccharide antigens of type Ia and type Ib group B Streptococcus. Biochemistry 1983; 22:1258.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
