"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?9/25/9621/abstract/6\">",
"      Jennings HJ, Rosell KG, Katzenellenbogen E, Kasper DL. Structural determination of the capsular polysaccharide antigen of type II group B Streptococcus. J Biol Chem 1983; 258:1793.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?9/25/9621/abstract/7\">",
"      Wessels MR, Bened&iacute; WJ, Jennings HJ, et al. Isolation and characterization of type IV group B Streptococcus capsular polysaccharide. Infect Immun 1989; 57:1089.",
"     </a>",
